        "description": "<p>Easy School Registration is a tool to help you manage your school registrations. Add your teachers, waves\/semesters and courses, open and close registration at specifed times, keep track of payments and other information in one place. The plugin was originally created for dance schools, but is applicable to all types of schools.<\/p>\n<p>For dance schools, the system automatically pairs partners by their emails and keeps classes balanced. Students can be notified with customizable emails that are sent automatically.<\/p>\n<p>The interactive registration form automatically checks if registration for the wave is open and does not allow registration before that time and date. The form can be customized to match the colors of your website.<\/p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/9TXBoDJbNeo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"><\/iframe><\/span>\n<h4>Features<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Simple &amp; Intuitive<\/li>\n<li>Couples pairing<\/li>\n<li>Interactive registration form<\/li>\n<li>Highly customizable<\/li>\n<li>Automated e-mails<\/li>\n<li>No limits for waves\/semesters, teachers, courses or students<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Links<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/easyschoolregistration.com\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Website<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/easyschoolregistration.com\/demo\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Demo<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/easyschoolregistration.com\/documentation\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Documentation<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/Domaneni\/easy-school-registration\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Github<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "installation": "<p>From your WordPress dashboard<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Visit<\/strong> Plugins &gt; Add New<\/li>\n<li><strong>Search<\/strong> for &#8220;Easy School Registration&#8221;<\/li>\n<li><strong>Activate<\/strong> Easy School Registration from your Plugins page<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='are%20there%20any%20limitations%20for%20this%20plugin%3F'>\nAre there any limitations for this plugin?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p><strong>NO<\/strong> This plugin is free, and you can use it on as many sites as you want with no limit on the number of waves\/semesters, teachers, courses or students<\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>3.9.8 2024-01-23<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Option to rename solo course title<\/li>\n<li>New &#8211; New registration validation filter<\/li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Translations loading<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.9.7 2023-10-28<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; New user registration form (enabled by settings)<\/li>\n<li>New &#8211; Lots of new currencies<\/li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Partner Selection Required description<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.9.6 2023-07-16<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Removed user field (user_firstname) that is not used already<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.9.5 2023-06-26<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Registration enforce partner was wrongly validated<\/li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Already registered override function was wrongly validated<\/li>\n<li>Add &#8211; Option to split student name to first name and surname in admin tables<\/li>\n<li>Add &#8211; Option to hide couples settings and data in administration<\/li>\n<li>Add &#8211; Support for variables in styling settings<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.9.4 2023-06-05<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; WordPress translations load<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.9.3 2023-04-09<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add &#8211; Option to enable multiple registrations to same course by the same user<\/li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Log table column names<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.9.2 2022-11-15<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update &#8211; Currency setup and added new Thai Baht currency<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.9.1 2022-09-05<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Fix names for options that prevented saving settings<\/li>\n<li>Update &#8211; Payment table display changed to action calls<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/easy-school-registration\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2775752\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/easy-school-registration\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2775752\" alt=\"&lt;p&gt;Registration form on frontend&lt;\/p&gt;\"><\/a><p><p>Registration form on frontend<\/p><\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/easy-school-registration\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2775752\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/easy-school-registration\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2775752\" alt=\"&lt;p&gt;Administration for adding new course&lt;\/p&gt;\"><\/a><p><p>Administration for adding new course<\/p><\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/easy-school-registration\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2775752\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/easy-school-registration\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2775752\" alt=\"&lt;p&gt;List of registrations in administration&lt;\/p&gt;\"><\/a><p><p>List of registrations in administration<\/p><\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/easy-school-registration\/assets\/screenshot-5.png?rev=2775752\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/easy-school-registration\/assets\/screenshot-5.png?rev=2775752\" alt=\"&lt;p&gt;Emails setting page&lt;\/p&gt;\"><\/a><p><p>Emails setting page<\/p><\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/easy-school-registration\/assets\/screenshot-6.png?rev=2775752\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/easy-school-registration\/assets\/screenshot-6.png?rev=2775752\" alt=\"&lt;p&gt;Styling setting page&lt;\/p&gt;\"><\/a><p><p>Styling setting page<\/p><\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">The best plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/mustafaomer\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/578cfc8b44095eeef8ab2ae98e8ae5ea?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/578cfc8b44095eeef8ab2ae98e8ae5ea?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/mustafaomer\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mustafaomer<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 31, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">The best plugin<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very handy for dance schools!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/katjad\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/db9c2d99c195362d2c520f32ae7ddea5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/db9c2d99c195362d2c520f32ae7ddea5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/katjad\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">katjad<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 7, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">We have been using this plugin for several years now and it saves us tons of time in the whole registration process! \n\nThe different features are perfect when organizing dance classes: having a quick overview to see what the numbers of leads and follows are, having access to all the details of the participants, easy access to transfer the data to excel. But the best part of it for us is sending out the automatic emails for each step in the process: registration, access to to the classes, payments and payment reminders!\n\nRecently we had our first 'problem' with the plugin but it was due to our own setup\/ outdated versions and we were very much pleasantly surprised of the quick and thorough support we received! Thank you so much!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
    },
    "short_description": "Kiss goodbye to Google Forms and other incomplete tools \u2013 manage your dance school within your WordPress!",
